---
title: Fig-Maple Pork Tenderloin with Broccoli and Garlic Roasted Potatoes
description: Pork loves making friends with a sweet sauce. Tonight, juicy, pan-seared and oven-finished pork tenderloin pairs up with a lip-smackin' good fig-maple sauce to put a smile on your face! Garlicky roasted potatoes and buttery broccoli make this a beautifully composed plate.
